  participant Client
  participant API as API Service
  participant VECTOR as Vector DB

  Client->>API: GET /images/{image_id}/similar
  API->>VECTOR: Fetch embedding vector by image_id
  VECTOR-->>API: Return vector
  API->>VECTOR: Submit vector for similarity search
  VECTOR-->>API: Return similar image_ids + scores
  API-->>Client: Return similar images with scores
